HEADWORD: Enfouldred
<hw>En*foul"dred</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>en-</ets> + OF. <ets>fouldre</ets>, <ets>foldre</ets>, lightning,
F. <ets>foudre</ets>, L. <ets>fulgur</ets>.]</ety> <def>Mixed with, or
emitting, lightning.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧With foul
<xex>enfouldred</xex> smoke.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
